<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 2, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 3; Metro Desk 
