<TEXT>
<P>
 GE Denies Talks on American Express Bid: General Electric Co. denied a 
published report that its GE Capital Services unit may be seeking to acquire 
American Express Co.Business Week magazine reported that a senior American 
Express employee and an investment banker, both unidentified, said the GE unit 
