<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 2, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2; Column 3; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
