ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Biomerica Inc.: The medical diagnostic products maker Thursday restated 
results for its latest fiscal year. 
</P>
<P>
 The company, based in Newport Beach, said it earned $56,491, rather than 
having the previously reported loss of $82,253. The company said the revision 
was because of an accounting change. 
</P>
<P>
 The change means that, for the fiscal year ended May 31, the company's 
shareholders earned 1 cent a share. For the previous fiscal year, Biomerica 
reported a loss of $435,244. 
</P>
