</P>
<P>
 Quietly had quality performance a year ago with 9 1/2 sacks in 15 starts. Has 
knack for making the big play and has produced 29 1/2 sacks in last 68 games. 
Knee injury sidelined him in training camp, but his recovery is essential to 
team's hopes for strong start on defense. 
</P>
