</P>
<P>
 Ram season went asunder as soon as Young went down with knee injury. Team 
looked like it might have one of league's best front four with Young picking up 
seven sacks in first four games. Young's injury allowed teams to double 
Gilbert, thereby nullifying push up the middle. 
</P>
