 How about that Ram offense? Rams failed to score touchdown in four games last 
season, didn't score more than 10 points in eight games. Zendejas, however, had 
a banner year, hitting 16 of 23 field goals, including six from 50 yards or 
beyond. Presently fifth in all-time kicking percentage (.745) 
</P>
