like our chances." Allison and Vit split time at quarterback last season and 
are again battling for the job. "I'm real pleased with the contest," Clark 
said. "They both have been working a little harder." Another heated competition 
is occurring at tight end. Mann and Tafua have both been impressive, which 
might force Clark to rotate them and devise plays using two tight ends. 
