PREP FOOTBALL '94 / GOLDEN WEST LEAGUE; TUSTIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 1993 RECORDS 
</P>
<P>
 OVERALL: 3-7 
</P>
<P>
 LEAGUE: 1-6 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 COACH: Tim Ellis 
</P>
<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 3-7 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 RETURNING STARTERS 
</P>
<P>
 OFF: 3 
</P>
<P>
 DEF: 4 04,26,05,05,05 TOP RETURNERS OFF DEF YR Ricky Cherry, 5-8, 165 -- DB 
Sr. Reggie Curry, 6-2, 180 WR DB Sr. Chris McDonald, 5-9, 170 -- DB Sr. Brian 
Roberts, 6-2, 180 WR -- Sr. Adam Stadler, 6-0, 180 -- LB Jr. Mike Staubly, 6-2, 
